author_ssm: Megan O'Shea and Molly A. Cross
unittitle_ssm: Tamiment Library and Robert F. Wagner Labor Archives Collection of Health Serials
abstract_ssm: The Tamiment Library and Robert F. Wagner Labor Archives Collection of Health Serials contains over 50 titles on physical and mental health issues, medical professionals, and social and political issues related to health in the United States and other countries.  The collection dates between 1936 and 2004, with the bulk of the material dating from the 1980s through the 1990s.
